1: # AI-DLC (AI-Driven Development Life Cycle)
7: AI-DLC is an intelligent software development workflow that adapts to your needs, maintains quality standards, and keeps you in control of the process. For learning more about AI-DLC Methodology, read this [blog](https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/devops/ai-driven-development-life-cycle/) and the [Method Definition Paper](https://prod.d13rzhkk8cj2z0.amplifyapp.com/) referred in it.
9: ## Table of Contents
12: - [Platform-Specific Setup](#platform-specific-setup)
23: - [Experimental: AI-Assisted Setup (Release Download)](#experimental-ai-assisted-setup-release-download)
29: ## Common
31: 1. Download the latest release zip file named `ai-dlc-rules-v<release-number>.zip` from the [Releases page](../../releases/latest) to a folder **outside** your project directory (e.g., `~/Downloads`).
32: 2. Extract the zip. It contains an `aidlc-rules/` folder with two subdirectories:
33:    - `aws-aidlc-rules/` — the core AI-DLC workflow rules
34:    - `aws-aidlc-rule-details/` — detailed rules conditionally referenced by the core rules
35: 3. Follow the setup instructions for your coding agent and platform below.
