500: ### OpenAI Codex
502: AI-DLC supports OpenAI Codex as a supported coding agent, using the [Codex AGENTS.md](https://developers.openai.com/codex/guides/agents-md) convention to deliver its intelligent workflow. Codex automatically discovers and loads `AGENTS.md` from your project root when you start a session.
509: cp ~/Downloads/aidlc-rules/aws-aidlc-rules/core-workflow.md ./AGENTS.md
511: cp -R ~/Downloads/aidlc-rules/aws-aidlc-rule-details/* .aidlc-rule-details/
