729: - Verify rules are listed in the Amazon Q Chat Rules panel
732: #### Cursor
735: - Check **Cursor Settings → Rules** to ensure the rule is enabled
736: - If rule is too large (>500 lines), split into multiple focused rules
738: #### Cline
740: - Check the Rules popover under the chat input field
743: #### Claude Code
748: #### GitHub Copilot
752: - Check that `.github/copilot-instructions.md` exists in your workspace root
